OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry evening with some late spells of
OL,7,Fsunshine, especially in the east.
OL,8,FOvernight remaining dry although cloud
OL,9,Fincreasing and the breeze freshening
OL,10,Fin the west towards dawn with a few
OL,11,Fspots of rain.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FA bright start, but cloud will
OL,14,Fcontinue to build from the west. Rain
OL,15,Fwill reach western coasts by mid-
OL,16,Fmorning before gradually spreading
OL,17,Feastwards throughout the rest of the
OL,18,Fday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
